description: Aino Health AB engages in the provision of health and safety management solutions. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 28 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-12-16. The firm operates as a provider of corporate health management (CHM) solutions. The firm's Aino HealthManager solution allows organizations to monitor their personnel’s working capacity and the impact of different measures. The firm's Aino SafetyManager platform provides safety management tools. The firm's Aino HealthDesk solution is a multichannel service designed for employee's sick leave related issues. Its TeleHealth solution offers remote occupational health care visits. In addition, the Company provides various services, such as business process outsourcing and health management consulting services, among others.
naics: Management, Scientific, and Technical Consulting Services
